---
title: Indian-Inspired Turkey Burgers with Spiced Fries and Cucumber Raita
description: These burgers pack a powerful flavour-fusion punch! Herby, Indian-spiced turkey patties are topped with sautéed peppers and cooling cucumber raita, all sandwiched between sweet brioche buns. Don't forget to dip the spiced fries in leftover raita for an addictive creamy, crispy combo!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-dinde-a-lindienne-dd6ecbde.jpg
